# Exported CircuiTikZ symbol SVGs — build artifacts regenerated by
# tools/export_circuitikz_svgs.py and baked into manifest.json (the only
# committed asset). Some filenames (e.g. D*.svg) contain characters that are
# illegal on Windows, so they must not be tracked. The manifest is kept.
tools/circuitikz_svgs/**/*.svg
